FBIS3-23345 "jptot013__l94026" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 LATIN AMERICA MEXICO `Pacifist' Writer Arrested for Killing Candidate Colosio Presidency Confirms Death PA2403050194 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0438 GMT 24 Mar 94 PA2403050194 Mexico City XEW Television Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Presidency of the Republic has confirmed the death of Luis Donaldo Colosio, presidential candidate for the Institutional Revolutionary Party.
